text: Cicuiara striata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was first described by Henry Walter Bates in 1866 as Exocentrus striatus. It is found in Brazil and Venezuela.BioLib.cz - Cicuiara striata. Retrieved on 13 May 2020. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1866
